### Create Supplier
POST http://localhost:3000/api/suppliers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplierId": "SUP001",
  "companyName": "Green Materials Co",
  "contactPerson": "Ahmed Ali",
  "email": "supplier1@example.com",
  "phone": "+966501234567",
  "address": "King Road",
  "city": "Riyadh",
  "country": "Saudi Arabia",
  "products": ["cement", "steel"]
}

###

### Get All Suppliers
GET http://localhost:3000/api/suppliers

###

### Search Suppliers
GET http://localhost:3000/api/suppliers/search?term=cement